'''''Typhoon Thompson in Search for the Sea Child''''' is a video game created by [[Dan Gorlin]].  It was published by [[Broderbund]] for the [[Atari ST]] in 1988, then the [[Amiga]] in 1990. ''Typhoon Thompson'' is a reworking of the [[Apple II series|Apple II]] game ''[[Airheart]]'', also written by Gorlin.

==Reception==
The game was ranked the 24th best game of all time by ''[[Amiga Power]]''.<ref>Amiga Power magazine issue 0, [[Future Publishing]], May 1991</ref>

